      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S PUMPKIN (3) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from nine starts. Scored by 4 lengths last time (19.63) in a Grade 5 over 366m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. CRICKLE OWL VIC (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing sixth (20.09) at this track latest. Has a good record here at this journey. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Worth following up. DAYSEA'S ELVIS (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Pop Said Yes (20.02) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. UNACCEPTABLE PAT (6) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
